00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:03,370
Who did this?

568
00:30:03,710 --> 00:30:04,960
Li Zhangyi...

569
00:30:05,600 --> 00:30:08,120
He claimed Yunge is a Yao State spy

570
00:30:08,610 --> 00:30:10,670
and forced the madam to hand her over.

571
00:30:11,430 --> 00:30:12,390
Yunge...

572
00:30:13,590 --> 00:30:15,050
Is she the one with a sachet

573
00:30:15,190 --> 00:30:17,650
