574
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:19,920
That was my gift to her.

575
00:30:20,840 --> 00:30:22,840
Yanzhi is my name.

576
00:30:23,230 --> 00:30:25,160
Yunge would never do that.

577
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:28,000
She's been wrongly accused.

